    {
      "id": "egtx99Smukwp6w5MVIgr_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1885.4355626578495,
      "y": 249.43882407610297,
      "width": 320.255859375,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1841699756,
      "version": 93,
      "versionNonce": 2078157460,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1721886292324,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1 - First store the head into a current ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1 - First store the head into a current ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "x9kQAluV3OOPAXd-NJf4R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1885.0753283758731,
      "y": 432.05442102441543,
      "width": 544.0797119140625,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 632023188,
      "version": 317,
      "versionNonce": 1640600748,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1721880835095,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2 - now we have to make this first group as a individual linked list \n    by breaking the kth node link and preserver the next node  ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2 - now we have to make this first group as a individual linked list \n    by breaking the kth node link and preserver the next node  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OhZiSb8yapddYSdUa093q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1892.5616222924064,
      "y": 664.989412966274,
      "width": 573.5836791992188,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1MV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 698525996,
      "version": 633,
      "versionNonce": 838717076,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1721886316407,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3 - now we call the reverse function and reverse the first group\n we have to reuse it so we will make a separate function for it pointer\nposition  will remain same ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3 - now we call the reverse function and reverse the first group\n we have to reuse it so we will make a separate function for it pointer\nposition  will remain same ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kjutpkcCFfiflCx-KXzij",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1886.5438601599722,
      "y": 965.0850928304756,
      "width": 621.919677734375,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1Ml",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 650372116,
      "version": 888,
      "versionNonce": 836065708,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1721880835095,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4 - We now this that the kth node will always be our new head but remember \n    the initial head will always be updated for the first group ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4 - We now this that the kth node will always be our new head but remember \n    the initial head will always be updated for the first group ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "z4uPRmYXE-gLAi9eeiMgE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2532.6707658381597,
      "y": 190.50172621920058,
      "width": 721.8076171875,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1Mt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 966728620,
      "version": 1275,
      "versionNonce": 1230495404,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1721886391427,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5  now we have to repeat the same process for the 2nd kth group by shifting the current\n   to the next ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
